<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Transfer – PharmaChain</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen">
  <%- include('_nav') %>

  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-700 mb-2">🔄 Supply Chain Flow</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6">Follow these steps in order. Each role uses a different MetaMask account.</p>

    <div id="walletInfo" class="hidden bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-200 rounded-lg p-3 mb-6 text-sm text-indigo-700">
      👛 <strong id="walletAddress"></strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; 🌐 <strong id="networkName"></strong>
    </div>
    <button id="connectBtn" onclick="connectWallet()"
      class="bg-indigo-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded mb-6 hover:bg-indigo-700">
      🔗 Connect Wallet
    </button>

    <!-- Flow Steps -->
    <div class="space-y-4">

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-5 border-l-4 border-indigo-400">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <span class="bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded">Account 1 — Manufacturer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">Step 1: Add Medicine</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Create medicine on blockchain with all details.</div>
        <a href="/add" class="inline-block bg-indigo-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded text-sm hover:bg-indigo-700">
          ➕ Go to Add Medicine
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center text-gray-400 text-xl">↓</div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-5 border-l-4 border-yellow-400">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded">Account 1 → Account 2</span>
        </div>
        <div class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">Step 2: Assign Distributor</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Manufacturer ships medicine to distributor.</div>
        <a href="/distributor" class="inline-block bg-yellow-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded text-sm hover:bg-yellow-600">
          🚚 Go to Distributor Dashboard
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center text-gray-400 text-xl">↓</div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-5 border-l-4 border-green-400">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded">Account 2 — Distributor</span>
        </div>
        <div class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">Step 3: Confirm Receipt + Send to Pharmacy</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Distributor confirms receipt, then sends to pharmacy.</div>
        <a href="/distributor" class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded text-sm hover:bg-green-700">
          ✅ Go to Distributor Dashboard
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center text-gray-400 text-xl">↓</div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-5 border-l-4 border-purple-400">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded">Account 3 — Pharmacy</span>
        </div>
        <div class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">Step 4 & 5: Mark Available + Sell</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Pharmacy marks medicine available then sells to customer.</div>
        <a href="/pharmacy" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded text-sm hover:bg-purple-700">
          💊 Go to Pharmacy Dashboard
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center text-gray-400 text-xl">↓</div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-5 border-l-4 border-gray-400">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded">Customer — Any Account</span>
        </div>
        <div class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">Step 6: Verify Medicine</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Customer scans QR or enters Medicine ID to verify authenticity.</div>
        <a href="/verify" class="inline-block bg-gray-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded text-sm hover:bg-gray-700">
          📱 Go to Verify Page
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('_loading') %>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/ethers/5.7.2/ethers.umd.min.js"></script>
  <script>const CONTRACT_ADDRESS = "<%= CONTRACT_ADDRESS %>";</script>
  <script src="/ui.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
